<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Match Assignment Notification</title>
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			background-color: #f4f4f4;
			padding: 20px;
		}

		.container {
			background: #ffffff;
			padding: 20px;
			border-radius: 10px;
			text-align: center;
			box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		h2 {
			color: #333;
		}

		p {
			color: #555;
		}

		.notification {
			font-size: 18px;
			font-weight: bold;
			margin: 20px 0;
		}
		.assigned {
			color: #28a745; /* Màu xanh lá cây */
		}
		.removed {
			color: #dc3545; /* Màu đỏ */
		}

		.match-details {
			text-align: left;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		.footer {
			margin-top: 20px;
			font-size: 12px;
			color: #999;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
	<h2>Match Assignment Notification</h2>
	<p>Dear {{umpireName}},</p>
	<div class="notification {{#if isAssigned}}assigned{{else}}removed{{/if}}">
		You have been {{#if isAssigned}}ASSIGNED{{else}}REMOVED{{/if}} from the following match:
	</div>
	<div class="match-details">
		<p><strong>Tournament:</strong> {{tournamentName}}</p>
		<p><strong>Event:</strong> {{tournamentEvent}}</p>
		<p><strong>Match Number:</strong> {{matchNumber}}</p>
	</div>
	<p>
		{{#if isAssigned}}
			Please be prepared to officiate this match. Further details and any updates will be communicated to you.
		{{else}}
			This assignment has been removed. Please check your schedule for any other assignments.
		{{/if}}
	</p>
	<p>If you have any questions, please contact the tournament organizers.</p>
	<div class="footer">
		&copy; 2025 Smash League. All rights reserved.
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>